@startuml
[*] --> Idle

Idle --> AdjustTime : Adjust Time
Idle --> AdjustAlarm : Adjust Alarm
Idle --> ToggleAlarm : Toggle Alarm
Idle --> ToggleLight : Toggle Light

AdjustTime --> Idle : Done
loop:AdjustTime : Increase Value

AdjustAlarm --> Idle : Done
loop:AdjustAlarm : Increase Value

ToggleAlarm --> AlarmOn
AlarmOn --> AlarmRinging : Alarm Time Reached
AlarmRinging --> AlarmOff : Stop Alarm

ToggleLight --> LightOn
LightOn --> LightOff : Light Released
LightOff --> LightOn : Light Pressed Again

AlarmOff --> Idle : Dismiss
AlarmOff --> [*] : Dismiss
@enduml
